ns-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\">Underperforming Sectors:</span></strong>\r\n        <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc; color: initial; font-family: initial; font-size: initial;\">\r\n            <li style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;\"><strong>IT:</strong> Experiencing pressure on margins as a result of the global slowdown in enterprise technology spending.</li>\r\n            <li style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;\"><strong>Metals:</strong> Weighed down by the lacklustre demand in China.</li>\r\n            <li style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;\"><strong>Real Estate:</strong> Sales and the launch of new projects are being slowed down by interest rate uncertainty.</li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Investors should monitor both sector performance and macroeconomic trends in order to better time their entries and exits.</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\'margin: 8pt 0cm 4pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 21px; font-family: \"Aptos Display\", sans-serif; color: rgb(15, 71, 97); font-weight: normal;\'><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Investor Strategies in a Volatile Market</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">How should astute investors respond with so many variables at play?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: C